text: Amy Coney Barrett’s ascent to the Supreme Court is not yet assured — but it could have earth-shaking consequences for American law https://t.co/PGa2WvkrI7

name: politico
text:
Years from now, President Donald Trump’s divisive rhetoric, his haphazard hirings and firings, even his tweets, will all eventually fade into memory. Other presidents will erase his executive orders.

His Supreme Court picks, however, will stay. https://t.co/5X63EeylzH
